## FN combinations
XF86Launch1
	xset dpms force off
XF86AudioMute
	lmc m
XF86AudioMicMute
	pactl set-source-mute 1 toggle
XF86AudioLowerVolume
	lmc down 5
XF86AudioRaiseVolume
	lmc up 5
XF86MonBrightnessDown
	light -U 15
XF86MonBrightnessUp
	light -A 15
